OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGraduates in England facing
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftax rise by stealth, says  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FIFS                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Graduates in England face a "stealth"  
OL,6, tax rise as the earnings threshold at  
OL,7, which they start repaying student loans
OL,8, is to be frozen, researchers say.      
OL,10,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies says a
OL,11,Fgraduate earning #30,000 will now repay
OL,12,F#113 more a year than expected.        
OL,14,FThe government said the freeze, coming 
OL,15,Finto effect in April, would help       
OL,16,Fmaintain the stability of the student  
OL,17,Floan system.                           
OL,19,FThe threshold increased in line with   
OL,20,Faverage earnings in previous years.    
